{"tid":744204,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"平行時空，當港隊贏得世界盃","createTime":"2018-07-15T19:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T19:48:45.000Z","uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f566114a4075dc69ec9938e170eab5e640906efa","tid":744204,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T19:34:06.000Z","msg":"2018年 香港成立21週年，先後陪育出C朗，美斯，仲有港隊，今年港隊打到入世界盃四強，<br />\n但觀眾舉的係兩面旗，到底邊一面旗先係代表到香港，有人話:「香港人舉香港旗。」，又有人話：「都是一樣的」咁既然一樣，點解又唔舉同一枝旗呢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n克羅地亞，加泰羅利亞，新加玻<br />\n西藏，蒙古<br />\n<br />\n而你，又諗到啲咩呢"},{"pid":"2b36ed29482063b80eb2db4ec3d6d8c3fcc65b28","tid":744204,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T19:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港開埠唔只100年"},{"pid":"bb857dce7d4b55a36ed60a3d3e7d515e2c96728e","tid":744204,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2b36ed29482063b80eb2db4ec3d6d8c3fcc65b28","tid":744204,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T19:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港開埠唔只100年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T19:36:56.000Z","msg":"太直接"},{"pid":"7e16af4944c9dec06a8abdd442152ce5ba0e1900","tid":744204,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T19:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}